org.sakaiproject.tool.messageforums.ui

Class MessageForumSynopticBean.DecoratedCompiledMessageStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.tool.messageforums.ui.MessageForumSynopticBean.DecoratedCompiledMessageStats
  • Enclosing class:
    MessageForumSynopticBean

    public class MessageForumSynopticBean.DecoratedCompiledMessageStats
extends Object
    Used to store synoptic information for a users unread messages. Whether on the Home page of a site or in MyWorkspace determines what properties are filled.

    If in MyWorkspace, each object contains the number of unread Private Messages and number of unread Discussion Forum messages.

    If in the Home page of a site, each object contains either the number of unread Private Messages or number of unread Discussion Forum messages.

    Author:
    josephrodriguez
